title: Creature with the Crystal Skin
itunes:title: Creature with the Crystal Skin
description:
It is dark inside the human body, but not every denizen of the animal kingdom is such a closed book. In this episode of Stuff to Blow Your Mind, Robert and Joe discuss various creatures with transparent anatomical features and translucent bodies.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
